name: Amystory
overview:
Amystory.com is online dating site when it launched on the Web in 2008. Amystory.com is an free online dating service specifically geared toward the Asian community, and is one of the amazing sites for Asian singles to find their match. This singles online community is dedicated to helping Filipino, Korean, Chinese, Indonesian, Japanese and other Asian men and women to meet singles in a comfortable online environment.

Amystory.com is a source for creating relationships ranging from companionship to friendship, romance to marriage. Amystory.com focuses on providing a clean, safe, and friendly environment where you can meet, date, and create relationships through their online dating blog, mini log, video, live chat, private mailbox, and more.
